title: Peter Thomas Roth AHA/BHA Acne Clearing Gel 2 fl oz
description: A potent medicated oil-free blemish clearing gel for the prevention and treatment of acne. Contains maximum strength beta hydroxy acid (salicylic acid 2%) and potent alpha hydroxy acid (glycolic acid complex 10%).  Oil-free, fragrance-free deep pore clearing gel, exclusively formulated to clear up whiteheads, acne blemishes and blackheads, re-fine pores and reduce the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles. Helps regulate healthy cell turnover for a clear, flawless complexion.

title: Bioelements Beyond Hydration, 2.5-Ounce
description: An oil-free moisturizing gel that acts like a "second skin" to prevent moisture loss. Helps support and strenghten skin as it provides hydration and prevents moisture loss. Comfortable to wear, refreshing and non-greasy, it won't clog pores or cause breakouts.

title: 15pcs Nail Art Painting Pen Brush
description: Package includes : 3x Drawing Tools 7x Painting Tools (also can use as gel nail curing brush) 2x Liners 1x Dotting Tool 2x Fan brushes for nail art effect (also can use as eye shadow brush)
